This project was started in April 2008, to try and replace the no-longer-updated site [http://www.passthefracp.com Pass the FRACP]. It is intended to be a reference for candidates for the written and clinical examinations, and provide a source of: * Exam wisdom from those that have gone before * Resources for candidates (study notes etc).
