'''<big>Examples</big>'''

How about aspects?

Here's a stack:

    function stack()
        {
        var store = :null;

        function push(item)
            {
            store = cons(item,store);
            item;
            }
        function pop()
            {
            var item = car(store);
            store = cdr(store);
            item;
            }
        function empty?()
            {
            store == :null;
            }
        this;
        }

----

