==== cosh ====

{{C++ Programming/Syntax|
<source lang=cpp>
#include <cmath>
float cosh( float arg );
double cosh( double arg );
long double cosh( long double arg );
</source>
}}

The function cosh() returns the hyperbolic cosine of ''arg''.

;Related topics: [[C++ Programming/Code/Standard C Library/Functions/acos|acos]] - [[C++ Programming/Code/Standard C Library/Functions/asin|asin]] - [[C++ Programming/Code/Standard C Library/Functions/atan|atan]] - [[C++ Programming/Code/Standard C Library/Functions/atan2|atan2]] - [[C++ Programming/Code/Standard C Library/Functions/cos|cos]] - [[C++ Programming/Code/Standard C Library/Functions/sin|sin]] - [[C++ Programming/Code/Standard C Library/Functions/sinh|sinh]] - [[C++ Programming/Code/Standard C Library/Functions/tan|tan]] - [[C++ Programming/Code/Standard C Library/Functions/tanh|tanh]]

